{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I found a very nice place for her, and I left her there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Unfortunately, barely a few weeks I'm at home, and she just couldn't adjust.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she asked me to come back, which I did the second time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she stayed on a little while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I came back again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then in April I went to get her and brought her back to New York.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She stayed with us a little while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Unfortunately we don't have an extra room for her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We tried to get her something, but by then her health seemed to fail.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She had a heart condition, and we thought that the best thing would be to put her somewhere where she could get some care.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was this beautiful brand new nursing home in Queens, and I was able to get her a lovely room, and she was quite happy there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But she didn't stay long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She became ill, we took her to the hospital, and she never returned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She died of heart failure August 27, 1977.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a very special piece of jewelry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a young girl in Italy, of course, I had nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as every young girl wants some jewelry, but they couldn't afford.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had these $3 among us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, when we lived in Ostia Lida di Roma, my aunt managed to buy this on the beach of Ostia for $0.25 American.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it became my absolute one and only and most favorite piece.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was restrung many, many times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But needless to say, I would not trade it with a necklace of diamonds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Have there been any decisions you've made or things you've done that were influences by your Shoah experience?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think everything I do, in a way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My outlook on life, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
